data.description: Welcome to Bergen Place! This 4-bed, 2.5-bath home with new paint and carpet throughout is ready for new owners. Inside, you'll find the kitchen that includes ample counter space, kitchen island and breakfast area. Spacious living room features a fireplace and the formal dining room is the perfect place to entertain guests. Half bath also located on the main floor for guest access. Enjoy your morning coffee in the sun room looking out to your privacy fenced backyard. Unwind at the end of the day in your owner's suite with a jacuzzi bathtub, double vanity and walk-in closets. Three additional bedrooms and hall bath with double vanity and shower/tub combo also located upstairs. Step onto the back deck and enjoy the fully landscaped yard, perfect for the summer months. With its prime location, spacious layout, and desirable features, this home is a must see!
